Class AttributeBean

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.shale.clay.config.beans.AbstractBean
      org.apache.shale.clay.config.beans.SymbolBean
          org.apache.shale.clay.config.beans.AttributeBean
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable
public class AttributeBean
extends SymbolBean
implements Serializable

Represents a value for a component property or a tag attribute. Instances of this class will be placed in the ComponentBean attributes collection.

See Also:
Serialized Form
